## EC2 Setup

1. Launch an Ubuntu EC2 instance with a Public IP
2. Configure Security Group Inbound Rules:

| Type  | Port | Source    |
|-------|------|-----------|
| SSH   | 22   | Your IP   |
| HTTP  | 80   | 0.0.0.0/0 |
| HTTPS | 443  | 0.0.0.0/0 |

3. SSH into your EC2:

```bash
ssh -i your-key.pem ubuntu@<your-ec2-public-ip>
```

