## Nginx Configuration

Edit the default Nginx config:

```bash
sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/default
```

Paste this configuration:

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;

    # Serve Frontend
    location / {
        root /home/ubuntu/testing-purose/frontend;
        index index.html;
    }

    # Proxy Backend
    location /backend/ {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:3000/;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
    }
}
```

Fix file permissions:

```bash
sudo chmod 755 /home/ubuntu
sudo chmod 755 /home/ubuntu/testing-purose
sudo chmod 755 /home/ubuntu/testing-purose/frontend
sudo chmod 644 /home/ubuntu/testing-purose/frontend/index.html
```

Test and restart Nginx:

```bash
sudo nginx -t
sudo systemctl restart nginx
sudo systemctl enable nginx
```

